e\nintroduced by ATLAS in MicroMegas and developed here for the first time for\ntriple-GEM detector. A complete triple-GEM simulation software has been\ndeveloped to improve the knowledge of the detection processes. The software\nreproduces the CGEM-IT behavior in the BESIII offline software.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Apr 2019 13:44:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-16"}
