nce of Convex (DC) programming. Finally, numerical results show the\nadvantage of the proposed solutions over existing ones, and demonstrate the\nimportance of the optimization of view synthesis-enabled multicast\nopportunities in MVV transmission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Apr 2019 03:19:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 28 Dec 2019 07:52:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-01"}
